In[70]:
trf1 = ColumnTransformer([
    ("Gender", OneHotEncoder(sparse_output=False, drop='first', handle_unknown="ignore"), ["Gender"]),
    ("ordinal_trf1", OrdinalEncoder(), ["Subscription Type"]),
    ("ordinal_trf2", OrdinalEncoder(), ["Contract Length"]),
    ('scale', MinMaxScaler(), make_column_selector(dtype_include='number'))  # Automatically selects numerical columns
])

    ('trf1',trf1),
    ('trf3',DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state = 42))
])

model = Sequential()

model.add(Dense(128, input_dim=10, kernel_initializer="he_normal", use_bias=False))
model.add(Dropout(0.3))
model.add(BatchNormalization())
model.add(Dense(64, activation = "relu"))
model.add(Dropout(0.3))
model.add(BatchNormalization())
model.add(Dense(32, activation = "relu"))
model.add(Dropout(0.3))
model.add(BatchNormalization())
model.add(Dense(16, activation = "relu"))
model.add(Dropout(0.3))
model.add(BatchNormalization())
model.add(Dense(1, activation = "sigmoid"))
In[106]:

callbacks = EarlyStopping(
    monitor = 'val_loss',
    min_delta = 0.00001,
    patience = 20,
    verbose = 1,
    mode = "auto"
    )
history = model.fit(x_train_transformed, y_train, epochs=500, validation_data = (x_test_transformed, y_test), callbacks = callbacks)
